.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, milk, sprite, water
House: cape-cod, victorian, craftsman, palace
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, april, july, august
4 different pets are kept: dog, frog, goldfish, rabbit
 1. the person who's birthday is in july is between the owner of the dog and the person who's birthday is in april##2
 2. the person drinking milk is not to the right of the owner of the frog##8
 3. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the cape-cod house##3
 4. the person drinking lemonade is not to the right of the owner of the rabbit##8
 5. the owner of the dog is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in april##8
 6. the palace house is not to the right of the person drinking water##8
 7. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere to the left of the owner of the rabbit##5
 8. the owner of the goldfish is in an odd position##4
 9. the person who's birthday is in november is the owner of the frog##1
10. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left or right of the owner of the dog##3
11. the owner of the dog is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in july##8
12. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
13. the person who's birthday is in august is somewhere to the right of the victorian house##5
14. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in july##3
15. the person drinking lemonade is on the far left or far right##3
16. the craftsman house is on the right of the cape-cod house##1
17. the person drinking lemonade is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in april##8
18. the victorian house is not to the right of the owner of the frog##8
19. the person drinking water is on the right of the victorian house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |   4   |
| Beverage      | lemonade | sprite | water  | milk  |
| House          | palace     | victorian | cape-cod | craftsman  |
| Birthday   | april    | july  | august | november |
| Pet           | goldfish | rabbit | dog    | frog  |

