 4. the person playing go is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
 5. the person watching disaster movies is not to the right of the polish##8
 6. the person playing bridge is not to the right of the person watching disaster movies##8
 7. the person playing backgammon is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in july##8
 8. the malaysian is the person watching drama movies##1
 9. the british is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in august##8
10. the person watching mystery movies is not to the left of the person watching disaster movies##8
11. the person playing poker is between the person who's birthday is in august and the person watching drama movies##2
12. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
13. the malaysian is not to the right of the person watching drama movies##8
14. the person playing backgammon is on the left or right of the person watching drama movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
