11. the person playing chess is on the right of the person playing go##1
12. the person playing snooker is not the argentine##6
13. the dutch is somewhere to the right of the person drinking sprite##5
14. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
15. the townhouse house is not to the right of the person playing snooker##8

